WEBVTT

00:03.360 --> 00:04.952
(BEEPING)

00:06.000 --> 00:09.754
# <i>I can see clearly now</i>
<i>the rain has gone</i>

00:09.880 --> 00:13.509
JAMIE: <i>See that?</i>
<i>That's what's gonna kill everyone.</i>

00:13.640 --> 00:16.074
<i>Any second now.</i>

00:16.200 --> 00:20.512
<i>Yeah. It's Judgment Day.</i>
<i>The actual apocalypse.</i>

00:20.640 --> 00:22.551
<i>And where am I? In Slough.</i>

00:22.680 --> 00:25.148
<i>Or, rather, under Slough.</i>

00:25.280 --> 00:27.669
NEWSREADER:
<i>One minute, now. One minute.</i>

00:27.800 --> 00:29.995
<i>These pictures</i>
<i>coming live to us from Hubble.</i>

00:30.120 --> 00:34.159
<i>I mean, what the hell</i>
<i>are we all gonna do down here?</i>

00:34.280 --> 00:36.396
<i>No internet.</i>

00:36.520 --> 00:38.033
<i>No radio.</i>

00:38.160 --> 00:40.549
<i>God, I hope there's Boggle.</i>

00:40.680 --> 00:43.990
<i>It's time to brace ourselves.</i>
<i>To say goodbye.</i>

00:45.000 --> 00:51.074
